# Add additional owners as the project grows
# Format:
# /path/to/directory/ @github-username
# /specific/file.ext @github-username

# Multiple owners can be specified:
# /path/ @owner1 @owner2 @owner3

# Teams can also be used (requires organization):
# /path/ @org/team-name
